'''圣训捍卫者'''（Ansar al-Sunna）是活跃在[[莫桑比克|莫桑比克]][[德尔加杜角省|德尔加杜角省]]的一个[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰]]激进团体<ref name="PolGeo">{{Cite web|title="Islamic State" in Mozambique? Control Map & Timeline of the Insurgency|url=https://www.polgeonow.com/2020/08/northern-mozambique-isis-crisis-control-map-2020.html?m=1|accessdate=28 August 2020|author=Centanni|date=17 August 2020|first=Evan|work=PolGeoNow.com|publisher=Political Geography Now|archive-date=2022-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323012620/https://www.polgeonow.com/2020/08/northern-mozambique-isis-crisis-control-map-2020.html?m=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该团体經常對當地安全部队和平民發動袭击，企图在该地区建立一个[[伊斯兰国_(政权形式)|伊斯兰国家]] <ref>{{Cite web|title=Mozambique: Islamist Raids Continuing in Mocimboa Da Praia|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201712050740.html|accessdate=27 December 2017|date=5 December 2017|work=AllAfrica.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226234748/http://allafrica.com/stories/201712050740.html|archivedate=2017-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="APMoz">{{Cite web|title=Battle looms in Mozambique over extremists’ control of port|url=https://apnews.com/2f191b65e6f4157562e906c1965065d6|accessdate=28 August 2020|author=Bowker|date=25 August 2020|first=Tom|work=[[美联社|美联社]]|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101230107/https://apnews.com/2f191b65e6f4157562e906c1965065d6|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ARMoz">{{Cite web|title=Mozambique: Sophistication of Islamic insurgency threatens LNG plans|url=https://www.theafricareport.com/38238/mozambique-sophistication-of-islamic-insurgency-threatens-lng-plans/|accessdate=28 August 2020|author=MacDonald|date=24 August 2020|first=Andrew|work={{link-en|The Africa Report}}|publisher={{link-en|Jeune Afrique}}|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108032610/https://www.theafricareport.com/38238/mozambique-sophistication-of-islamic-insurgency-threatens-lng-plans/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。圣训捍卫者的成员大多是莫桑比克人，主要来自[[濱海莫辛布瓦|濱海莫辛布瓦]]、[[帕爾馬_(莫桑比克)|帕爾馬]]和[[馬科米亞區|馬科米亞區]]，但也有一部分来自[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]和[[索马里|索马里]]。該組織成員会讲莫桑比克的官方语言[[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]、莫桑比克的当地语言{{link-en|姆瓦尼語|Mwani language}}和[[大湖地区|大湖地区]]的通用语言[[斯瓦希里语|斯瓦希里语]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=População captura supostos membros do grupo armado que atacou Mocímboa da Praia|url=http://www.verdade.co.mz/newsflash/63770-populacao-captura-supostos-membros-do-grupo-armado-que-atacou-mocimboa-da-praia-|accessdate=27 December 2017|work=Verdade.co.mz|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226234801/http://www.verdade.co.mz/newsflash/63770-populacao-captura-supostos-membros-do-grupo-armado-que-atacou-mocimboa-da-praia-|archivedate=2017-12-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

该团体是由[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]激进宗教人士{{link-en|阿布德·罗戈|Aboud Rogo Mohammed}}的追随者在[[德尔加杜角省|德尔加杜角省]]组建。2012年阿布德·罗戈死亡後他的追隨者來到莫桑比克定居。该團體從2017年開始愈發暴力<ref name="jamestown140618">{{Cite web|title=Ansar al-Sunna: A New Militant Islamist Group Emerges in Mozambique|url=https://jamestown.org/program/ansar-al-sunna-a-new-militant-islamist-group-emerges-in-mozambique/|accessdate=15 September 2018|date=14 June 2018|work=Jamestown Foundation|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616202851/http://jamestown.org/program/ansar-al-sunna-a-new-militant-islamist-group-emerges-in-mozambique/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年，圣训捍卫者宣布向[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]效忠。该团体的资金主要来自非法走私[[象牙|象牙]]、[[木材|木材]]、[[毒品|毒品]]和[[红宝石|红宝石]]等產品以及[[人口販賣|人口販賣]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=非洲多地面临严峻安全挑战|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-09/02/c_1210781337.htm|accessdate=|author=新華網|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212020824/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-09/02/c_1210781337.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc020618">{{Cite web|title=How Mozambique's smuggling barons nurtured jihadists|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-44320531|accessdate=15 September 2018|date=2 June 2018|work=BBC News|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513084603/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-44320531|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

圣训捍卫者武装分子曾受到莫桑比克前警察和前边防士兵的培訓，這些前警察和士兵因被解雇所以对政府怀恨在心，故而支持該團體。该團體还联系东非的其他伊斯兰武装分子，据说他们从[[索马里|索马里]]、[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]和[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]請來了[[青年党_(索马里)|青年党]]的教官負責培訓<ref name="Former Policemen">{{Cite news|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201805010190.html|title=Mozambique: Former Policemen Train Islamist Group|date=2018-05-01|work=Agencia de Informacao de Mocambique (Maputo)|accessdate=2018-06-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141112/http://allafrica.com/stories/201805010190.html|archivedate=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。圣训捍卫者的成員还前往其他地方接受當地好战团体的培训<ref name="extremist threat">{{Cite news|url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2018-05-31-is-northern-mozambique-faced-with-an-emerging-extremist-threat/#.WxgqqiAuCUl|title=Is northern Mozambique faced with an emerging extremist threat?|author=Jasmine Opperman|work=Daily Maverik|date=31 May 2018|accessdate=6 June 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612152612/https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2018-05-31-is-northern-mozambique-faced-with-an-emerging-extremist-threat/#.WxgqqiAuCUl|archivedate=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

